comments_data.body:
@MegamindLS this crash log is incomplete, and i wonder why.
the stack trace part is empty, and the info output part only contains the server and memory sections.
do you happen to know why?
i also see the command that caused the crash is `DELTREE`, there's no such command in redis.
are you using some redis module in your deployment?
anything else you can tell us about how to reproduce this?
i see you're using a 64 bit ARM, and that redis is built for 32 bits.
anything else you can tell us about this platform and build?
